{"type":"message","id":"3bd20801","parentId":"1bf59876","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:19.978Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 16:02 CDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Message for Beckham: Tony says he loves the team. Start now on Replit integration: identify top 3 blockers and concrete fixes for canonicalization/build path."}],"timestamp":1773090139974}}
{"type":"message","id":"951f17bc","parentId":"3bd20801","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:24.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Message for Beckham: Tony says he loves the team.\n\nFor the Replit integration regarding canonicalization/build path, here are the top 3 blockers and concrete fixes:\n\n1. Blocker: Inconsistent or ambiguous canonical paths across the build system.\n   Fix: Implement a centralized canonical path resolver that normalizes and validates all paths before use, ensuring uniform references throughout the build process.\n\n2. Blocker: Build path mismatches due to environment differences in Replit (e.g., container paths vs. local dev).\n   Fix: Add environment-aware path mapping layer that translates canonical build paths to the appropriate Replit container paths dynamically during build and runtime.\n\n3. Blocker: Lack of automated verification for canonicalized paths causing build failures.\n   Fix: Integrate a build-time verification step that checks the existence and correctness of all canonical paths, with detailed logs and automatic fallbacks if anomalies are detected.\n\nLet me know if you want me to proceed further or provide detailed implementation plans.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b15c74d3bc2659f0069af355cb3608197941946fed8111a45\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":8502,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8700,"cost":{"input":0.0034008000000000003,"output":0.0003168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037176}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090139977}}
